events.name: Google Certification for Web Developers
events.description: *********RSVP/Register at: https://peatix.com/event/375447********* The Mobile Sites (mSite) certification is a professional accreditation that Google offers to individuals, who demonstrate proficiency in basic and advanced aspects of mobile website design and development. A Mobile Sites certification allows individuals to demonstrate that Google recognizes them as an expert in mobile sites. Agenda:1-3 pm : Study Jam led by mSite Certified facilitators.3-5 pm : Attempt the free certification exam. Important Note:1. Bring your own laptop2. You need basic web development skills3. Study Jam is suitable for programmer with minimum of 3-6 months of experience in building web sites.3. Study Jam is focus on basic concepts. So may not be suitable for very experienced programmers.
